In this [Spanish name](/Spanish_name), the first or paternal [surname](/Surname) is Calderón and the second or maternal family name is Serra.

## Sila Calderón

Calderón in 2001

*   **[Governor of Puerto Rico](/Governor_of_Puerto_Rico)**
    *   **In office:** January 2, 2001 – January 2, 2005
    *   **Preceded by:** [Pedro Rosselló](/Pedro_Rossell%C3%B3)
    *   **Succeeded by:** [Aníbal Acevedo Vilá](/An%C3%ADbal_Acevedo_Vil%C3%A1)
*   **Mayor of [San Juan](/San_Juan,_Puerto_Rico)**
    *   **In office:** January 2, 1997 – January 2, 2001
    *   **Preceded by:** [Héctor Luis Acevedo](/H%C3%A9ctor_Luis_Acevedo)
    *   **Succeeded by:** [Jorge Santini](/Jorge_Santini)
