*   **Born:** Sila María Calderón Serra (1942-09-23) September 23, 1942 (age 83)
    *   [San Juan, Puerto Rico](/San_Juan,_Puerto_Rico)
*   **[Party](/Political_party):** [Popular Democratic](/Popular_Democratic_Party_(Puerto_Rico))
*   **Other political affiliations:** [Democratic](/Democratic_Party_(United_States))
*   **Spouses:**
    *   Francisco González (m. 1964; div. 1975)
    *   Adolfo Krans (m. 1978; div. 2001)
    *   Ramón Cantero Frau (m. 2003; div. 2005)
*   **Children:** 3, including [Sila](/Sila_Mar%C3%ADa_Gonz%C3%A1lez_Calder%C3%B3n)
